  <paragraphs>
    <title><custom ref="synthesis-actividad-titulo"/></title>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++++]</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Read the story together.</li>
      <li>Act out the story as a class using a student suggestion. After acting out the first verse, reread the second verse and ask: <q>¿Qué será diferente cuando actuemos la historia esta vez?</q>
      (Only two of the ducks came back.)
      </li>
    </ul>
  </paragraphs>


